early age, those close to the teacher said. As well as teaching first grade, Soto was also studying for a master's degree in special education at Southern Connecticut State University. She graduated from Eastern Connecticut State University with an elementary education and history degree. &quot;I have a passion for learning,&quot; she wrote on her <a href=\"http://myschooldesk.net/newtown/teachersite.aspx#site.7320_pid.31372_mid.55614\">online teacher's page</a>.</p><p>Soto listed her passions outside school as spending time with family members, along with her dog, a black Labrador named Roxie. Soto had been at the school for five years, first as an intern, then as a classroom teacher.</p><p>&quot;I look forward to an amazing year in the first grade with my amazing students of room 10!&quot; she wrote.</p><!-- Guardian Watermark: internal-code/content/401139040|2012-12-22T11:49:05Z|bd37f9ed5adf3c3841a5e339c442167a8c4b8f77 -->","showInRelatedContent":"true","lastModified":"2012-12-17T09:50:46Z","hasStoryPackage":"true","score":"1.0","secureThumbnail":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/audio/video/2012/12/15/1355592937441/A-sign-honouring-victims--005.jpg","standfirst":"First-grade teacher Soto, who had worked at the school for five years, reportedly died trying to shield her students from harm","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/3ch9a","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/audio/video/2012/12/15/1355592937441/A-sign-honouring-victims--005.jpg","wordcount":"322","commentable":"false","internalContentCode":"401139040","isPremoderated":"false","byline":"Matt Williams","publication":"guardian.co.uk","internalPageCode":"1843165","shouldHideAdverts":"false","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2012-12-18T18:47:11Z"},"tags":[{"id":"world/newtown-shooting","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webTitle":"Newtown shooting","webUrl":"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/newtown-shooting","apiUrl":"http://co